Wang Jiayi's transaction records?

29
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,040
No, that's fine.

30
00:02:29,290 --> 00:02:30,410
Okay, Mr. Sheng.

31
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,750
Jiayi, you look amazing today.

32
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:40,950
