34
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,080
What's going on?

35
00:02:43,950 --> 00:02:45,540
Sheng Shi, you're here.

36
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:47,790
Nothing much.

37
00:02:47,870 --> 00:02:48,580
They were just saying

38
