39
00:02:54,450 --> 00:02:55,290
Let me see.

40
00:03:00,290 --> 00:03:01,370
Yeah, it's nice.

41
00:03:01,910 --> 00:03:03,000
Really nice.

42
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:05,830
The design's good,

43
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:09,700
but honestly, Miss Wang,

44
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:12,080
it's kind of wasted on you.

45
00:03:13,290 --> 00:03:14,410
What a pity.

46
00:03:18,540 --> 00:03:21,000
Did you give Chengchi that tie?

47
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:23,500
Last time, you embarrassed Chu,

48
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:24,700
