54
00:04:06,790 --> 00:04:07,660
En.

55
00:04:08,620 --> 00:04:09,500
Here.

56
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,000
Have some warm water.

57
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,200
I added a little ginseng

58
00:04:13,330 --> 00:04:14,500
to help you relax.

59
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:28,950
Are you sure there's nothing going on?

60
00:04:29,660 --> 00:04:30,910
Then why did you both use

61
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,870
the phrase "My Chengchi"?

62
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:35,750
Don't you remember?

63
00:04:36,700 --> 00:04:38,410
You were the one

64
00:04:38,620 --> 00:04:40,200
who came up with it.

65
00:04:41,290 --> 00:04:42,620
Really?

66
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:43,910
Yes.

67
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,750
Back in high school,

68
00:04:46,870 --> 00:04:48,250
you, me,

69
00:04:48,410 --> 00:04:50,120
Shi, and Shan,

70
00:04:50,620 --> 00:04:52,620
